libisoburn is a frontend for libraries libburn and libisofs
which enables creation and expansion of ISO-9660 filesystems
on all CD/DVD/BD media supported by libburn.
This includes media like DVD+RW, which do not support
multi-session management on media level and even
plain disk files or block devices.

Interface pour les bibliothèques libburn et libisofs
permettant la création des système de fichiers ISO-9660
sur tous les CD/DVD/BD. 

